WEBVTT

00:04:30.456 --> 00:04:31.846
And in the office,

00:04:31.870 --> 00:04:35.132
we wanted to create an environment
where people treated each other

00:04:35.156 --> 00:04:37.307
just a little bit better,

00:04:37.331 --> 00:04:40.997
just a little bit more
respect and consideration

00:04:41.021 --> 00:04:42.624
than in the outside world.

00:04:44.740 --> 00:04:49.645
And we continued to iterate
and collaborate and find solutions

00:04:49.669 --> 00:04:52.962
to create things that hadn't been seen.

00:04:54.530 --> 00:05:00.066
